# 5.2 Gamma-Poisson conjugate family


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
# Plot the Gamma(10, 2) prior
plot_gamma(shape = 10, rate = 2)
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](05_notes_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-1-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
plot_poisson_likelihood(y = c(6, 2, 2, 1), lambda_upper_bound = 10)
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](05_notes_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-2-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
plot_gamma_poisson(shape = 10, rate = 2, sum_y = 11, n = 4)
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](05_notes_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-3-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
summarize_gamma_poisson(shape = 10, rate = 2, sum_y = 11, n = 4)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}
```
      model shape rate mean     mode       var        sd
1     prior    10    2  5.0 4.500000 2.5000000 1.5811388
2 posterior    21    6  3.5 3.333333 0.5833333 0.7637626
```
:::
:::


# 5.3 Normal-Normal conjugate family


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
plot_normal(mean = 6.5, sd = 0.4)
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](05_notes_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-5-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
# Load the data
data(football)
concussion_subjects <- football %>%
  filter(group == "fb_concuss")

concussion_subjects %>%
  summarize(mean(volume))
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}
```
  mean(volume)
1       5.7346
```
:::

```{.r .cell-code}
ggplot(concussion_subjects, aes(x = volume)) + 
  geom_density()
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](05_notes_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-6-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
plot_normal_likelihood(y = concussion_subjects$volume, sigma = 0.5)
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](05_notes_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-7-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
plot_normal_normal(mean = 6.5, sd = 0.4, sigma = 0.5,
                   y_bar = 5.735, n = 25)
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](05_notes_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-8-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
summarize_normal_normal(mean = 6.5, sd = 0.4, sigma = 0.5,
                        y_bar = 5.735, n = 25)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}
```
      model mean mode         var         sd
1     prior 6.50 6.50 0.160000000 0.40000000
2 posterior 5.78 5.78 0.009411765 0.09701425
```
:::
:::
